long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Which is different with Mahjong or other block puzzle game. Tile Master Match consists a large number of levels that get progressively more difficult.

INTRODUCTION
Play Tile Master Match on your Google Chrome Browser with our simple & lightweight extension - No Internet required, no ADS, and 100% Free!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Tile Master Match extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Tile Master Match icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Tile Master Match popup will open. 
That's all you need to do! Have fun!

HOW TO PLAY?
Match 3 blocks of the same element, you will pass the level when all tiles are matched
